title: Toll Brothers Misses Orders Estimates Amid Slow Housing Market
description: Toll Brothers Inc. fell short of analysts’ estimates for quarterly orders, signaling that fewer people are signing contracts to build homes as high prices and economic uncertainty hold some buyers back.
